data.description: NO HOA! Would you like a home with personality? 1102 Westwood Drive is located in an older, established community that is super close to multiple commuter options, Mary Washington Hospital, shopping, and Old Town Fredericksburg.  A custom-built, all brick rambler with a full basement on a level lot! The basement includes a large recreation room with kitchen & bar area, 2 additional NTC  bedrooms & a full bath. Could be used for rental or Airbnb space. Oversized (23'11" x 20'3") 2.5 car garage. NEW Roof, doors, floors, paint, hardware, lighting, bathrooms, kitchens, appliances & more!
